      section.sg-sect
        h2 The Float Grid
        p.
          The Float Grid works just like the Flex Grid object above, except that this object
          is supported by legacy browsers such as #[cite Internet Explorer 9] and below.
        p.
          The container must have the #[code.sg-code .o-GridFloat] class and
          each item must have the #[code.sg-code .o-GridFloat__Item] class.
